            <a class="open" href="javascript:void(0)">p069 McVries motivates Olson to not give up</a>
            <div style="display:none">
                <p>&ldquo;Our first boneyard,&rdquo; McVries said. &ldquo;It&rsquo;s on your side. Ray, you lose all
                    your points. Remember that game?&rdquo;<br />&ldquo;You talk too goddam much,&rdquo; Olson said
