        <li class="gad msg mdg">
            <a class="open" href="javascript:void(0)">p298 Garraty almost dies #6 (fainting), McVries saves Garraty #4
                (distraction)</a>
            <div style="display:none">
                <p>He caught up with McVries, who glanced around. &ldquo;I thought you were out of it, kiddo,&rdquo;
                    McVries said.<br />&ldquo;So did I.&rdquo;<br />&ldquo;That close?&rdquo;<br />&ldquo;About two
                    seconds, I think.&rdquo;<br />McVries pursed a silent whistle. &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t think I&rsquo;d
                    like to be in your shoes right now. How&rsquo;s the leg?&rdquo;<br />&ldquo;Better. Listen, I
                    can&rsquo;t talk. I&rsquo;m going up front for a while.&rdquo;<br />&ldquo;It didn&rsquo;t help
